    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.283538>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1. Conus leopardus (ZSI / ANRC- 7444). 2. SEM of radular tooth of C. leopardus, 3. SEM of radular tooth of C. litteratus. 4. Shows dull white siphon with a black band and foot sole of living C. leopardus, 5. Shows pinkish or flesh coloured siphon mottled with dark red and foot sole of living C. litteratus. 6. C. litoglyphus (ZSI / ANRC- 7443). 7. C. striatellus (ZSI / ANRC- 7793). 8 & 9. C. coffeae (Fig. 8: ZSI / ANRC- 7795). Scale bars: 1: 35 mm; 2: 500 µm; 3: 200 µm; 6, 7, 8 & 9: 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/283538/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

